			</classificationInformation>
			<CASNumber>21645-51-2</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Aluminum hydroxide is used to treat heartburn, upset stomach, sour stomach, or acid indigestion. It is also used to reduce phosphate levels in people with certain kidney conditions. It is amphoteric, meaning it occurs as both basic and acidic in nature. It is found naturally as the mineral gibbsite and its three polymorphs bayerite, doyleite and nordstrandite. It is commonly used as an over-the-counter antacid.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">氢氧化铝用于治疗胃灼热、胃部不适、胃酸或胃酸过多。它还可用于降低某些肾病患者体内的磷酸盐含量。氢氧化铝具有两性，这意味着它在自然界中既是碱性的，也是酸性的。它在自然界中以矿物 gibbsite 及其三种多晶体 bayerite、doyleite 和 nordstrandite 的形式存在。它通常用作非处方抗酸剂。</common:generalComment>
			<sumFormula>Al(OH)3</sumFormula>
